<quantity box="[1216,1299,1097,1124]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" unit="mm" value="10.0">10 mm</quantity>
pedicel, turning red before drying brown, total size 13 × 
